{"tid":571780,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"十 年 前 嘅 林 欣 彤 已 經 盡 顯 白 滑 肌 膚！","createTime":"2018-02-25T04:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T02:29:59.000Z","uid":173320,"like":18,"dislike":88,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d3fdc75f28f932e11deaf2099ce6de49d13642fb","tid":571780,"uid":173320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:09:03.000Z","msg":"十年前林欣彤已經喺十八區超新聲歌唱比賽大SHOW佢嘅白滑美肌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直係玉女接班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pi3ZKVy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fpi3ZKVy.png&h=a938ab21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HRTD4hM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHRTD4hM.png&h=917b51b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UKbrsRI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUKbrsRI.png&h=0b59fb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時嘅佢只係穿上一條吊帶長裙已經殺曬<br />\n唔似以家嘅港女咁<br />\n又熱褲又短裙又化濃妝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yDFKkwi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyDFKkwi.png&h=86c1361e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時佢個樣都仲係好PURE AND TRUE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做女朋友都真係一流<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1xOtars.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1xOtars.png&h=ff17f623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到佢白滑小手臂, 又有啲肉哋<br />\n真係好想MEET下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qHpMO7H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqHpMO7H.png&h=917b0a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n初出茅廬嘅佢台風一啲都唔輸蝕<br />\n比賽中段好辛苦行到去前面標完高音<br />\n又即刻轉身射個三分波行返去後面<br />\n真係估佢唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xjUx7Pl.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxjUx7Pl.png&h=950005f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唱到高音時仲不忘望住自己心口仔以防走光！<br />\n<br />\n最後當然係以大熱姿態贏到開巷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連超級巨聲一既冠軍何紫慧只係亞軍！<br />\n<br />\n原片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0z58y4oKRMU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0z58y4oKRMU&d=XyEbFIQmaurJHCY37uFycNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=ee65716f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0z58y4oKRMU</a>"},{"pid":"183f842e0e8c95bbc2136464f342cc8c2bf97dd8","tid":571780,"uid":61075,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"喂你冷靜啲先"},{"pid":"1076f3afbc13ea38f7241f3d3ed750780a6c5630","tid":571780,"uid":51041,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"依家好撚正wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f68633809974738fabb16f07dba4dc9f7e20c10","tid":571780,"uid":173320,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"183f842e0e8c95bbc2136464f342cc8c2bf97dd8","tid":571780,"uid":61075,"like":99,"dislike":2,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"喂你冷靜啲先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"喂你又有幾冷靜？"},{"pid":"cc7faf3f3823a49d6b4052a24dce5c8021812d92","tid":571780,"